//! Status: stable
//! Description: A bare type annotation `HashMap<f64, i64>` on a record field
//! must be rejected at the type-annotation site with `BoundsNotSatisfied`.
//! Regression guard that the admissibility predicate's bound-failing branch
//! is reached from `validate_concrete_hashmap_type`, not silently accepted.

type Config {
    points: HashMap<f64, i64>;
}

fn main() {}
